data.text:
Full EastEnders characters list with photos and character bios when available. List contains all EastEnders main character names and features lead EastEnders roles. If you're looking for the most famous EastEnders characters then you're in the right place. This EastEnders main character list includes pictures of EastEnders characters and features useful character information like the names of actors or actresses who play the characters. EastEnders character roles from every season are included, along with the characters' gender, occupation and more.

A list made up of items like Jack Branning and Phil Mitchell.

This list answers the questions "what are the EastEnders characters called?" and "who are all the characters in EastEnders?"

You can click each image for a larger picture of the character, and in some cases you can click the character's name for a more detailed description. View the list of EastEnders character names as an info list or customize your view by switching to slideshow or blog mode. Share the list of the highly notable EastEnders characters by clicking the Facebook or Twitter icons. This list of most well-known EastEnders characters can also be sorted alphabetically if you click the header at the top of the column labeled "Name."

If you're looking for more minor EastEnders characters, then they should also be on this list, but if not feel free to add them below.

You may want to copy this fact-based list to build your own just like it, re-rank it to fit your views, then publish it to share with your Facebook friends, Twitter followers or with any other social networks you use regularly. {#nodes}
